{"tid":133111,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"地價都二萬二蚊一呎 起好之後賣幾多","createTime":"2017-02-24T10:34:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-24T12:44:11.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8402c021db63b3701bc6fcc3409cc7086225557c","tid":133111,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T10:34:07.000Z","msg":"又係中資以本傷人<br />\n<br />\n地政總署公布，鴨脷洲利南道住宅地以168.5578億港元批出，中標財團為龍光地產(03380)與合景泰富(01813)，每方呎樓面地價22,117元，較估值上限高出10.6%。 <br />\n<br />\n龍光地產指，高興首次成功投得香港地皮，認為鴨脷洲地皮為市區大型純海景住宅地皮，儘管地皮總價刷新香港地王紀錄，但公司認為該純海罕有，單價屬市場合理水平。同時，由於是次夥拍合景泰富競投，雙方雖未公布分帳佔比，但強調公司現金流充裕，無資金壓力。"},{"pid":"bb6183d9963d4f214a998da433eefa369b73d32b","tid":133111,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T10:45:27.000Z","msg":"落嚟搶地  我諗係狗共唯一默許既合法走資 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d78f8109432b0a0d371fd326fd77d1ac0d89b0e9","tid":133111,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T10:46:34.000Z","msg":"成個島 有埋地鐵之後,   根本無敵 <br />\n<br />\n無架啦,   變左 富貴島"},{"pid":"70119b3e7a691a4629aca7a5a3d63b1517af9bc3","tid":133111,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T10:48:21.000Z","msg":"未必有關係"},{"pid":"72823a02aa8ab39759170157a6c60bd4e0783f9a","tid":133111,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T10:50:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未必有關係</blockquote><br />\n跌市咪囤住先"},{"pid":"ab0e14e78a67b13f93f69bc55cb4f75f9302ef3c","tid":133111,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T10:52:43.000Z","msg":"可想而知樓價根本唔會跌，政府都唔會批准。呢D內房集團，後台全部都係紅色家族，政府搞跌樓價即刻得罪領導。"},{"pid":"308200540423ca0fcc901f9b65ad591899c8a9f3","tid":133111,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"